Package: metopi
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.6), python3-tk, python3-pip
Maintainer: Rabiul Rahat
Description: A modern, cross-platform countdown timer
 Metopi is a sleek and modern countdown timer application
 featuring color themes, fullscreen mode, and sound notifications.
 Perfect for presentations, cooking, or any timed activities.
